Hello! Thank you for calling West Barnstable Horse Hides. My name is Jamie. How can I assist you with your billing today?

Hi Jamie, I have a question about a recent charge on my bill.

I'd be happy to help with that! May I have your name, please?

Sure, it's Alex Thompson.

Thank you, Alex. Can you please provide me with the billing account number associated with your account?

Yes, the account number is two one four three six seven eight.

Great, thank you! Could I also have the last four digits of the billing phone number for verification?

Of course, it's five five two zero.

Thank you for that information, Alex. Let me pull up your account. I see that the charge in question was for lane time on a busy night, which resulted in a premium rate. Does this resolve your query?

Ah, I see. That makes sense, thank you for clarifying, Jamie.

You're welcome! If you have any more questions or need further assistance, feel free to call back. Thank you for your time, and have a great day!
